"title": "5914: optimism",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5914: optimism",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The ability to face the future with confidence. For believers this is possible because of their knowledge of God.</p>\n<h2>Optimism resulting from faith</h2>\n<h3>Confidence in God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps52:8\">PSA 52:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps125:1\">PSA 125:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps25:4-Ps25:5\">PSA 25:4–25:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps56:4\">PSA 56:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps71:5\">PSA 71:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps91:2\">PSA 91:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Nah1:7\">NAM 1:7</a></p>\n<h3>Confidence in what God can do</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:10-2Cor1:11\">2CO 1:10–1:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps27:1-Ps27:3\">PSA 27:1–27:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer17:7\">JER 17:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic7:7\">MIC 7:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:6\">HEB 13:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:14\">1JN 5:14</a></p>\n<h3>Confidence in what God will do in the future</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:5-2Cor5:8\">2CO 5:5–5:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts24:14-Acts24:15\">ACT 24:14–24:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:5\">GAL 5:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:3-Phil1:6\">PHP 1:3–1:6</a></p>\n<h3>Confidence founded on God's grace</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa12:1-Isa12:2\">ISA 12:1–12:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra10:2\">EZR 10:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor3:4-2Cor3:5\">2CO 3:4–3:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:12\">EPH 3:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:16-2Thess2:17\">2TH 2:16–2:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:21-1John3:22\">1JN 3:21–3:22</a></p>\n<h2>Encouragements to be optimistic</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:1\">JHN 14:1</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:13\">ROM 15:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps9:10\">PSA 9:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:3-Ps37:5\">PSA 37:3–37:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps42:5\">PSA 42:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps115:9-Ps115:11\">PSA 115:9–115:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:27\">JHN 14:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:33\">JHN 16:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:12\">ROM 12:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:17\">1TI 6:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb4:15\">HEB 4:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:19-Heb10:23\">HEB 10:19–10:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:13\">1PE 1:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:28\">1JN 2:28</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of optimism</h2>\n<h3>In the OT</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr32:8\">2CH 32:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:25\">PRO 12:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov31:11\">PRO 31:11</a></p>\n<h3>The apostle Peter</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:10\">1PE 5:10</a></p>\n<h3>The apostle Paul</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor7:4\">2CO 7:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:8-1Cor1:9\">1CO 1:8–1:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor4:17\">1CO 4:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:7\">2CO 1:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor2:3\">2CO 2:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor8:22\">2CO 8:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:22\">PHP 2:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col4:9\">COL 4:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col4:12-Col4:13\">COL 4:12–4:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:12\">2TI 1:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phlm1:21\">PHM 1:21</a></p>\n<h3>The apostle John</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/3John1:3-3John1:5\">3JN 1:3–1:5</a></p>\n<h2>Misplaced optimism</h2>\n<h3>Trusting in anyone or anything other than God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps146:3\">PSA 146:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg9:26\">JDG 9:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam15:32\">1SA 15:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job6:20\">JOB 6:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job8:12-Job8:13\">JOB 8:12–8:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:7\">PRO 11:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer7:4\">JER 7:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer9:4\">JER 9:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer12:6\">JER 12:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer49:4\">JER 49:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer49:31\">JER 49:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek29:16\">EZK 29:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic7:5\">MIC 7:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor9:4\">2CO 9:4</a></p>\n<h3>Presumption</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek13:6\">EZK 13:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa58:4\">ISA 58:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer7:9-Jer7:10\">JER 7:9–7:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:9\">LUK 18:9</a></p>",
